result.name: Thalassic 泰尚泰國菜館

reviews.text: A fine dining restaurant mainly serves Thai cuisine. Famous dishes have Hainan chicken rice, oyster fried eggs and green curry chicken with rice. The price of a lunch, including main course, rice and drinks, varies from HK$60 to HK $75.
Decent thai restaurant with a value lunch menu set.
Excellent food! Lunch set is very reasonable. My favorite is the green curry! :)

Been going here for many years, still the Best Thai food in the area. 
Their lunch set is very good deal- the Laksa soup is best I've ever had! 
Keep it up!
Big portion for dinner even if I only ordered fried noodles. So end up I needed to take away for half of the portion because I couldn’t finish it!

result.name: 泰尚泰國菜館

reviews.text: 平時最愛泰國菜，也經常叫外賣，但今次個晚餐呢⋯⋯真係好難食，忍唔住要分享一下現在的心情！泰式炒河粉，係泰廚一到簡單都能炒得好的一味，但今晚嘗試的第一次的難食，毀滅咗我食晚餐的心情。河粉唔太完整，好容易斷，沒有口感，雞肉非常硬，整體無味道，希望會作出改善⋯⋯

A fine dining restaurant mainly serves Thai cuisine. Famous dishes have Hainan chicken rice, oyster fried eggs and green curry chicken with rice. The price of a lunch, including main course, rice and drinks, varies from HK$60 to HK $75.

Excellent food! Lunch set is very reasonable. My favorite is the green curry! :)

Been going here for many years, still the Best Thai food in the area. 
Their lunch set is very good deal- the Laksa soup is best I've ever had! 
Keep it up!
